description.narrative: Effective management of human resources capacity was maintained, with vacancies reduced, turnover and temporary rates decreased, and gender balance maintained at above global averages for D and E duty stations. PCO currently has 323 staff members on the ground. The ratio of staff categories remained stable during 2019: international professional staff 13 per cent, national staff: 53 per cent, and general service staff: 34 per cent, gender balance, however, remained a challenge. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
